  "title": "Discounted Cash Flow: If a property is expected to generate 120000 in NOI...",
  "summary": "Calculate or interpret NOI in real estate investment analysis.",
  "prompt": "If a property is expected to generate $120,000 in NOI for the next 3 years with a terminal value of $1,500,000 at the end of year 3, what is the NPV if the discount rate is 8%?",
  "options": [
    {
      "id": "A",
      "text": "7%"
